Package Entity

Class Index

java.lang.Object
Entity.Index
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Index
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
Represents an Index of a course. A course can have many indexes. Each index belongs to one course.
